# 2026-03-28 09:18:11.193241
+In kiro/voiquyr/src/agents/stt_agent.py, make these exact changes:
+
+1. After the last import line at the top of the file, add:
+   from langdetect import detect as langdetect_detect, DetectorFactory
+   DetectorFactory.seed = 0
+
+2. Find the method 'detect_language' inside the LanguageDetector class. Replace the ENTIRE method with:
+
+    async def detect_language(self, text: str) -> LanguageDetectionResult:
+        try:
+            detected_language = langdetect_detect(text)
+            return LanguageDetectionResult(
+                language=detected_language,
+                confidence=0.95,
+                dialect=None,
+                accent_region=None,
+            )
+        except Exception as e:
+            self.logger.warning(f'Language detection failed ({e}), defaulting to en')
+            return LanguageDetectionResult(
+                language='en',
+                confidence=0.5,
+                dialect=None,
+                accent_region=None,
+            )
+
+3. Find any line in process_audio_stream or similar that calls detect_language(chunk) or detect_language(audio_chunk) and change the argument to result.text

